Class PanoramaComputerBean

    public final class PanoramaComputerBean
extends java.lang.Thread
    A panoramaComputer bean allows for observation of it's parameters. It represents the current information that is being calculated.

      • PanoramaComputerBean

        public PanoramaComputerBean(ContinuousElevationModel cDem,
                            java.util.List<Summit> summitList)
        Creates the ComputerBean and sets the listener so that when the parameter changes the other variables are recalculated accordingly.
        Parameters:
        cDem - Continuous elevation model of the area where you will want to compute panorama.
        summitList - List of all the summits that you want to label.
